0918CD0A.Line13.789BF: Yours was even longer, it seems. Did you face your inner demons as the Horadrim did?

69E26198.Line15.BAE4: Yes. Hopefully for the last time.

6F245388.Line11.789BF: I don’t know yet. He wandered around for hours until the tea wore off. A long journey through the swamp is more rewarding than a short one.
